---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<!-- PLACEHOLDER: Replace with actual privacy policy -->
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Buzz Co Curbing"
  description="Privacy policy for Buzz Co Curbing. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-32 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <p class="font-data text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-warm-muted mb-4">LEGAL</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-section-heading font-bold text-dark mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none font-body text-dark/80 space-y-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-dark/50 italic">Last updated: [Date]. This is placeholder content. Replace with your actual privacy policy before launch.</p>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Information Collection</h2>
          <p>We may collect information you provide when you request an estimate, contact us, or use our website. This may include your name, phone number, email address, property address, and any details you share about your project.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Use of Information</h2>
          <p>We use the information you provide to respond to your inquiries, schedule estimates, perform services, and communicate with you about your project. We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Cookies and Tracking</h2>
          <p>Our website may use cookies and similar technologies to improve your experience, analyze site traffic, and support marketing efforts. You can adjust your browser settings to manage or disable cookies.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Third Parties</h2>
          <p>We may share information with service providers who assist us in operating our business (e.g., CRM, analytics, payment processors). These parties are required to protect your information and use it only for the purposes we specify.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Data Security</h2>
          <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal information. Contact us using the information on our website to exercise these rights.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through our <a href="/contact/" class="text-accent hover:underline">contact page</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
